Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:10.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:28.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:50.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:24:01.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之剑{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斩断这一昏暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:08.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,923)\fad(500,500)}莉拉·佛罗伦兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}リラ・フローレンツ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土里土气的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问你的感想 快说见没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看到他就通知我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到赏金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能离开这个垃圾堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏金？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉住他的人赏十万达卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一听到这个 连眼神都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穷光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家里堆满了破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 那可是她们的重要家具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些垃圾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那身衣服很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你从哪儿捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是从垃圾箱里捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服可是奶奶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我过生日的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1449,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}莉拉的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息传到了远在天城的哲力胥公爵耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已掌握了协助他逃走的反泰坦尼亚组织的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アルセス・タイタニア伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必很快就能把方修连捉拿归案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是方修连 是方修利 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为你太轻视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会如此失态的 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 那家伙已经逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拒绝了我们的招安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经对士兵们下令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现 格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在只是个叛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有异议吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯 这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也替我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叮嘱过您 不能来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许久不见了 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(696,923)\fad(500,500)}泰莉莎·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(696,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テリーザ・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们该不会是在吵架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人 我从心底尊敬着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会和哥哥吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 也对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可是世上唯一的亲兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利普提亚送来了好茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从利普提亚来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方送来了最高级的茶叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这孩子还是这么体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得跟亚瑟斯道个别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于刚才那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可千万不要妄下决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会给哥哥添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 亲爱的亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(723,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国皇帝 哈鲁夏六世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(723,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国皇帝 ハルシャ六世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利又逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手没能立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以伊德里斯卿才会这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真能成为救世主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫方修利的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进门之前先确认一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1182,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1182,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是道过歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴·鲍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹把门锁上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打火机不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗 是米兰达送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萨比安卡公国的贵族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫得蛮亲热的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是你们的老大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 戴·鲍尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里亚太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不把你赶出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能名垂青史了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经借由凯贝罗斯会战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给一潭死水注入了生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水已经开始流动了 没人能制止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 明天一早就走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你让我歇了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是通缉犯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上到处都是通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出门就会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车到山前必有路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 你是我们重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再玩革命游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是做不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老实工作 老实过日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不去奢望 应该能过得蛮幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少看不起人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不惜冒着生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了复兴卡萨比安卡公国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是在做游戏呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我说得太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾宾格王国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵也有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照顾这些小生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很费心费力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么公主大人 祝您做个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1040,923)\fad(500,500)}艾宾格王国 第二公主莉迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1040,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个方修利被捉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 连公主大人都开始在意他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若捉不到方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇就没法帮我养花了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 还没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但估计也快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 快点捉到他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方 不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天明明那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我和亚瑟斯伯爵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女人没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要开灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于露出本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受谁之托？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说戴·鲍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少敷衍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从女人身上吃了这么多亏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戴·鲍尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是另有其人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米兰达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下会让你做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为君尽忠可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但该守护的东西一定要守护好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到头来 痛苦的还是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和戴·鲍尔好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会来这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有善良市民通报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天来亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚伯爵府上一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十万达卡 一个子都不会少你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够这种生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军爷 另一个约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你孙女窝藏犯人的罪过一概不究
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧 莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从头再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你心意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不多说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短针枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的道具还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 快点离开这个星球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口处有两个把门的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走那边的窗户 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吻是宇宙第一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那边逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要顺利脱险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国军 亚朗·麦佛迪中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国軍 アラン・マフディー中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪边去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你们直追
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去右边搜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 忘带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 忘带东西了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄大人居然会这么大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能请你站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往对面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着手铐跑起来果然不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧 方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着一个身无分文的失业者有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关系着我的薪水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输 我认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 让我费这么大劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着那玩意的话 早晚会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还带着GPS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想被抓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1254,923)\fad(500,500)}米兰达·卡西米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1254,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公…公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 差点忘了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,923)\fad(500,500)}亚历亚伯特·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从第二代藩王 诺利殿下以来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的历代族长都很胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1340,923)\fad(500,500)}亚术曼·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1340,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们知道自己早晚也会走向没落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这次禁闭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历亚伯特卿的心境有什么变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还真得感谢方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来吧 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过了一个发大财的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴·鲍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你放走了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复兴卡萨比安卡的计划要从头再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有错 没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒星间货物船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式的名字是Honest Oldman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么听来还蛮平常的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像宾馆似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是正直老人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}康普顿·卡基米尔船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}コンプトン・カジミール船長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的喉咙有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法出声打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我再睡一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他的声带被毁掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为批判泰坦尼亚被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伯爵吗 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然承蒙你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有话在先
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对革命没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指复兴卡萨比安卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压根就没指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不像戴·鲍尔和莉拉那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对现在的生活还蛮满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么要救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想见见打赢泰坦尼亚的男人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心作祟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入正题吧 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船缺个事务次长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你担任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想离开这个星球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次长… 就是说还有事务长在咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过九个新年 那个活化石就活够一个世纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才需要人辅佐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是拒绝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有我选择的余地嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能离开这个星球就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊 中尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达 卡基米尔船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说来 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你们好像早就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢在那里悠哉悠哉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦佛迪中尉大人是个罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个黑商
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑商？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他常把军用物资倒卖给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 你们不也是走私商嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走私？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你陪我们走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得靠你的名号才好出航嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如离开这个破星球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往自由的宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快松开手拷放我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放你下船可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知物资外流的伯爵会怎么收拾你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然威胁我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你还挺会算账的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来做个会计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会计？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想下船的话请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 莉拉让我带给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 方修利提督离开了惑星艾曼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提兰基亚国王驾崩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息一出 流言四起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若手中的权力与身份不符
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些小人物只会被权力压垮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}憧憬与尊严


